                     <interp inst="t18200412-77-off439" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200412-77-off439" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, an the <rs id="t18200412-77-cd440" type="crimeDate">19th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200412-77-off439 t18200412-77-cd440"></join>, one cloak, value 3 l; one petticoat, value 5 s.; one tea-spoon, value 2 s., and eight pieces of silver money, value 2 s. 4 d., the property of 
                     <persName id="t18200412-77-victim699" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Cribb
                     <interp inst="t18200412-77-victim699" type="surname" value="Cribb"></interp>
