                     <interp inst="t18200412-77-person702" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am apprentice to Mr. Hulme, a pawnbroker, in Museum-street. On the 25th of January the prisoner pledged a tea-spoon and eight coins with me for 4 s.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
